I’m dedicated to helping companies keep their valuable data safe and sound. Every day, I work to spot the hidden risks, stop cyber attacks before they happen, and ensure the cloud systems run seamlessly and securely. My goal is simple: protect what matters most so businesses can thrive without worrying about security. If you want someone who’s both tech-savvy and committed to making cybersecurity proactive and approachable, that’s me!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>